@startuml
title Serverless Chatbot - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "IBM Cloud Functions" as CloudFunctions
participant "Assistant Function\n(assistant.js)" as AssistantFunc
participant "Watson Assistant" as Watson
participant "MongoDB Function\n(mongodb.js)" as MongoFunc
participant "MongoDB Database" as MongoDB

User -> CloudFunctions: Send message
activate CloudFunctions

CloudFunctions -> AssistantFunc: Trigger function with user input
activate AssistantFunc

AssistantFunc -> Watson: Send user input\n(create/manage session)
activate Watson

Watson -> Watson: Process NLP\n(intent recognition,\nentity extraction,\ndialogue management)

Watson --> AssistantFunc: Return response\n(output, intents, entities, context)
deactivate Watson

AssistantFunc --> CloudFunctions: Return Watson response
deactivate AssistantFunc

CloudFunctions -> MongoFunc: Trigger function with conversation data\n(input, output, intents, entities, context)
activate MongoFunc

MongoFunc -> MongoDB: Save conversation data
activate MongoDB

MongoDB --> MongoFunc: Acknowledge save
deactivate MongoDB

MongoFunc --> CloudFunctions: Confirm storage
deactivate MongoFunc

CloudFunctions --> User: Return chatbot response
deactivate CloudFunctions

@enduml
